        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
                <p><bibl><ptr target="#smith-porcher1864"/>, n. <citedRange>4</citedRange></bibl>, whence
                    <bibl><ptr target="#SGDI"/> <citedRange>4857</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#oliverioTacc"/>, <citedRange>XI.46, XIII.12</citedRange></bibl>, whence
                    <bibl><ptr target="#SECir"/> <citedRange>61</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>094200</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><persName type="attested" key="http://clas-lgpn2.classics.ox.ac.uk/cgi-bin/lgpn_search.cgi?id=V1-65763"><name nymRef="#Τεισίων">Τει<unclear>σίω</unclear>ν</name> <persName type="attested" key="http://clas-lgpn2.classics.ox.ac.uk/cgi-bin/lgpn_search.cgi?id=V1-64363"><name type="patronymic" nymRef="#Ἰάσων">Ἰάσονος</name></persName></persName>
	 </ab>
            </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
            
                <p>
                    <app loc="1">
                        <rdg resp="#smith-porcher1864">Τείσων <g type="punct">:</g> Ἰάσονος <note>there are no puncts but accidental holes</note></rdg>
                    </app>
                </p>
 </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="fr">
            <p>Teisiôn fils de Iasôn.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="en">
            <p>Teision son of Iason.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="it">
            <p>Teision figlio di Iason.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="ar">
            <p>تيسيون بن إياسون.</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>The base was associated with a statue which featured the man mentioned on its front face. To have it erected in Apollo's sanctuary was a honour.</p>
	<p/>
	<p/>
            </div></body>
